{"title":"【QZZ】HQY的蛋","time_limit":3000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4386","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>HQY特别喜欢吃蛋，尤其是<strong>她（他？）</strong>家母猪ZN下的蛋（一只特立独行的猪）。<strong>她</strong>家的老母猪ZN每天都会下一个蛋。但是，HQY在一次考试中考砸了，所以HQY只能把ZN下的蛋做成核弹、炸弹、子弹、或原子弹，忍痛割爱送给Teacher，（PS：这也能送？）希望能在下一次考试中得到高一点的分数。但是，Teacher在任意连续三天之内，不会接受同一种蛋。今天，HQY找到了会编程的你，想让你帮<strong>她</strong>算算，<strong>她</strong>在连续n天之内,<strong>她</strong>会有多少种送蛋的方法？<br></p><p><br></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>一个整数n，代表送蛋的天数。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数k，代表送蛋方法总数。<br/></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>24</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3&lt;=n&lt;=25</p><p>结果可能较大，时间可能很长。（你懂的哦！）</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}